      "content": "hey so im working on this new horror anthology and i need help with world building. i want to write a story set in a really gritty, urban part of a big city—like a place that feels heavy, maybe a bit dangerous and unpredictable, where you'd feel on edge just walking down the street at night. can u help me brainstorm some atmosphere and sensory details for a setting like that?",
