      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. i really want to lean into the \"danger\" aspect though. for this specific neighborhood, i want the tension to come from the people living there too. it's an area with a really high concentration of black residents, and i want to use that vibe to make the setting feel more intense and scary. maybe some way that the culture or the specific demographic of the area adds to that feeling of dread or unpredictability? how would u write that into the story?",
